For Emacs 22: "If the [[init file]] ##~/.emacs## does not exist, Emacs will try
##~/.emacs.d/init.el## or ##~/.emacs.d/init.elc##.  You can also put the shell
init file ##.emacs_SHELL## under ##~/.emacs.d##."

